title: DreadKnight Garen
body:
Using woobox I got:

- Alistar and his skin
- Tristana and her skin

But for one reason the DreadKnight Garen didn't work.
I tried a few times i decided to come here to tell u about this issue.(if i can name it issue)

Help me , please!

replies.body: Sorry for the trouble!  The Juggernaut has been added for you.  :D

If the link doesn't work, you can send a support ticket. Apparently you'll get a relatively fast automated response, and the skin should be added to your account.
